1. *Šališ* se sa svojim prijateljima često (You joke with your friends often).
2. On voli da *šali* o svemu (He likes to joke about anything).
3. Ona voli da *šali* sebi u lice (She likes to make fun of herself).
4. On ne šali sa nikim (He doesn't joke with anyone).
5. Ona uvek *šali* o svojim greškama (She always makes fun of her mistakes).
6. Deca se *šale* sa svojim roditeljima (The children joke with their parents).
7. Da li tvoji prijatelji *šale* se sa tobom? (Do your friends joke with you?).